            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Crispinus">Crispino</name></persName> filio
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Titus">Titoni</name></persName> (…) in proprio
                        territurio meo a fundamentis fabricis <rs key="#Private_foundations"
                            >construxi</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">eclesiam</rs> in honore Dei et <orgName
                            key="#Casalini/fundamenta #Size #Churches #Private_foundations"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/606">beati Sancti Martini</orgName>;
                            <foreign>ora le dona</foreign>: in primis <rs key="#Casalini/fundamenta"
                            >fundamento</rs> illo ubi ipsa Dei eclesia superposita est, qui est
                        tenente capite uno et uno latere in via publica, et alio latere est tenente
                        in <rs key="#Confinia #Petiae">terra</rs> de filii quondam <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae"><name key="#Confinia #Petiae" ref="Willeradus"
                                >Willeradi</name></persName> et alio capite tenet in <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae">terra</rs>
                        <persName><name key="#Confinia #Petiae" ref="Crispinus"
                            >mea</name></persName>, quod est per mensura <rs key="#Size">sistariorum
                            duodecim</rs>, in <placeName
                            key="#Casalini/fundamenta #Size #Churches #Private_foundations"
                            ref="#places/473">loco Ursiano</placeName>; et duas <rs key="#Petiae"
                            >petiolas </rs>de terra, qui mihi in <placeName
                            key="#Venditio #Petiae #Size" ref="#places/473">ipso loco</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Venditio">ex comparatione</rs> obvinet da <persName
                            key="#Venditio #Petiae #Size"><name ref="Domnichis"
                            >Domnichis</name></persName>, tras via, et inter ipsas petias percurret
                        semita publica, quod sunt plus minus <rs key="#Size">scafilorum tres</rs> in
                        integrum; et alia <rs key="#Petiae">petiola</rs> de terra mea ubi vocitatur
                            <placeName key="#Venditio #Petiae">ad Quarto</placeName>, qui genituri
                        meo <rs key="#Venditio">ex comparatione</rs> obvinet da quondam <persName
                            key="#Venditio #Petiae"><name ref="Deusdedit">Deusdede</name></persName>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/473">Lunata</placeName>, ipsa petia in integrum;
                        et alia <rs key="#Petiae">petiola</rs> de terra mea tras <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> nostra, qui est tenente
                        capite uno in via publica et in <rs key="#Rivers">rivo</rs> Caprio, ipsa
                        clausura plus minus <rs key="#Size">modiorum quinque</rs> in integrum; et
                        alia <rs key="#Petiae">petiola</rs> de terra mea, qui est similiter tenente
                        capite uno in ipsa via publica et in ipso <rs key="#Rivers">rivo</rs>
                        Caprio, et vocitatur <placeName ref="#places/486" key="#Petiae">ad Campora
                            communalia</placeName>, ipsa petia in integrum; et terra mea, qui est
                            <rs key="#Hay/fodder">prato</rs> et vocitatur <placeName
                            key="#Hay/fodder">Campo de <persName><name ref="Sintrualdus"
                                    >Suintruald</name></persName></placeName>, ipsa clausura in
                        integrum; et <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa</rs> mea ubi
                        vocitatur <placeName
                            key="#Venditio #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Cereals #Wine"
                            ref="#places/1016">ad Colli, prope Ruchi</placeName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Cereals">terra</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vinea</rs> et cum omnia
                        pertenente ad ipsa casa, qualiter mihi <rs key="#Venditio">ex
                            compartione</rs> obvinet de quondam <persName
                            key="#Venditio #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Cereals #Wine"><name
                                ref="Rado">Radoni</name></persName>. <foreign>Stabilisce inoltre
                            che</foreign> dum <persName><name key="#Priests" ref="Teutelmus"
                                >Teuselmi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>, filio meo, advivere meruerit <foreign>la
                            chiesa e i beni siano</foreign> in sua potestate regendi, gubernandi,
                        usufructuandi et officium Dei et luminaria in ipsa eclesia die noctuque
                        faciendi, caste et recto moderamine vivendi. <foreign>Se sopravvivesse al
                            figlio possa ordinarvi chi vuole. Se invece a sopravvivere fosse il
                            figlio</foreign>, in eius sit potestate in ipsa Dei eclesia ordinatione
                        faciendi de aliis filiis vel nepotibus meis quem ipse elegere voluerit aut
                        meliore previderit, nam non de extranei homenis; <foreign>e così
                            via</foreign>. Et post eorum decessu, volo adque instituo, ut ipsa Dei
                        eclesia sit in potestate pontifici illo qui hic Luca pro tempore <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> fuerit ordinatus <foreign>sempre con il
                            patto che egli nomini un esponente della famiglia come rettore, purché
                            ce ne sia uno disponibile e degno; altrimenti il vescovo scelga
                            liberamente il rettore. Scrive</foreign>: <persName
                            key="#Writer #Deacons"><name ref="Osprandus">Osprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>. (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            >Luca</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni</foreign>: + Crispini
                        donatori; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Priests"><name ref="Deusdedit"
                                >Deusdedit</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>; (ss) <persName key="#Witness #Priests"
                                ><name ref="Filosofronius">Filosofronius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs>; (ss) <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Raspertus"
                            >Raspert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs>; + <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Fuscus">Fusci</name></persName> filio quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Lupus">Lupi</name></persName> testis; + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name ref="Odo">Auti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerici</rs> testis.</ab>
                        </div>
